OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will see sunny
OL,6,Fspells with just a few showers.
OL,7,FThickening cloud will bring rain
OL,8,Facross all parts from the southwest
OL,9,Fduring this afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will clear away
OL,12,Fnortheastwards this evening. Then the
OL,13,Frest if the night will be largely dry
OL,14,Falthough with a lot of cloud. Fresh
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds. Mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA mainly dry day although
OL,18,Fwith a good deal of cloud. Some
OL,19,Fbrighter spells along the north coast.
OL,20,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
